data.description: The feeling of HOME is all around 18 Eastbranch Court!  The farmhouse style 2 story home has double fireplaces, a formal dining room and a flex space downstairs that is perfect for a 4th bedroom, home office or playroom. This beautiful home is located on over an acre of land on a quaint cul de sac, in the sought after neighborhood of Spring Valley.  Great schools, close to shopping and restaurants makes this a perfect fit for suburban living. Imagine sippin tea on the front porch, while watching the leaves change from season to season. This is HOME...YOUR HOME!!!! Seller offered closing cost assistance.
